NAME
    Text::Table::XLSX - Generate XLSX worksheet

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of Text::Table::XLSX (from Perl
    distribution Text-Table-XLSX), released on 2018-09-23.

SYNOPSIS
     use Text::Table::XLSX;

     my $rows = [
         # header row
         ['Name', 'Rank', 'Serial'],
         # rows
         ['alice', 'pvt', '123456'],
         ['bob',   'cpl', '98765321'],
         ['carol', 'brig gen', '8745'],
     ];
     print Text::Table::XLSX::table(rows => $rows, header_row => 1);

DESCRIPTION
    This module provides a single function, "table", which takes a
    two-dimensional array of data and generate an XLSX data stream from it.
    It's basically a very thin wrapper for Spreadsheet::GenerateXLSX.

